# App screenshots

Drop PNG or JPG files here, then add them to `site-config.js`:

```js
screenshots: [
  {
    src: "./assets/screenshots/main-ui.png",
    alt: "LyricsAI main window",
    caption: "Control panel with song queue and live preview",
  },
],
```

Recommended: 2–4 screenshots (main UI, live output, Bible/Sermon tab, slide queue).
